                    </div>

                    <p class="text-center text-[10px] font-semibold text-slate-500 leading-normal">Al guardar, se crearán tu catálogo público y tu panel privado.</p>
                    <button id="auth2-register-submit" type="submit" class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-500 text-white py-3.5 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider shadow-xl shadow-emerald-600/10 transition-all">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-store"></i>
                        Guardar y crear catálogo
